'''trumbe''' in [[Telerin]] means "shield". 
==Etymology==
The [[primitive Elvish]] form is given as ''[[turúmbê]]'' from [[TURÚM]] with the loss of an unaccented pre-stress vowel; such loss often occurs in the [[Common Telerin]]
==Cognates==
*[[Quenya]] ''[[turma]]''
*[[Sindarin]] ''[[turum]]''
